---
description: PHP-only constraints (no frameworks, no ORMs, no templating engines)
globs: **/*.php
alwaysApply: false
---

PHP constraints:

Use PHP standard library only.

Do not introduce:
- PHP frameworks
- templating engines
- ORMs
- dependency injection frameworks

Prefer simple PHP constructs:
- require / include
- plain classes and functions

Keep architecture minimal and explicit.
